$interpreted: Roger: Kittyeyes, are you alright?
Kittyeyes: I'm OK; but...
Roger: You're safe, that's all that matters. I was so worried that you would leave me just like that...
Kittyeyes: Roger, what's wrong...?
Roger: At first, I just treated you like a little sister. But, my feelings towards you are gradually...
General: What happened here? A single fire should not have caused this much damage...
General: Hmm? Aren't you...Roger? A wanted criminal of the Kingdom?
Roger: Damnit, the Kingdom army; what terrible timing...
General: Didn't expect to net such a major target on a simple inspection visit. Still, for a bandit as infamous as you, why this small village?
Old Man: W-We're innocent. We were threatened by Roger and had no choice but to take them in.
Male Villager: Yeah. You guys should take care of them, the quicker the better!
Kittyeyes: What nonsense are you people spilling!? We've been giving the village supplies all these years. How dare you people...
Roger: Kittyeyes, stop it. If that's the story they're going with, so be it...
General: I take that as confession for your crimes. If so, I'll have to take you down for the people! Men, get them!
Roger: Hmph, let's see if you really have what it takes to bring me down!
Kittyeyes: Roger, I'm coming to help!
Roger: Is your body feeling alright?
Kittyeyes: You don't have to worry about me. I'm more concerned about where we are gonna live from now on.
Roger: Once we get through this, let's find a place to live together in seclusion. And this time, we won't treat each other like siblings.
Kittyeyes: WHAT!? Does that...
Roger: Look out; here they come again!
Roger: You're one stubborn fella, ain't you!
General: It appears that you care a lot about the girl behind you. Once we capture her, you will have no choice but to surrender.
Roger: I dare you!

General: You don't have another hand to protect her now. 
Blame yourself for your own incompetence!
Kittyeyes: Bro Roger, NO!
